00:11:34.110 --> 00:11:36.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Communicator beeps ]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Kelby here.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:11:36.278 --> 00:11:37.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We're coming up on the comet.</i></c.bg_transparent>

201
00:11:37.696 --> 00:11:39.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm on it, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:11:40.116 --> 00:11:42.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is it, people. Cycle the ports.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:11:42.743 --> 00:11:45.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign, rig the intakes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for cometary debris.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:11:45.454 --> 00:11:47.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:11:49.333 --> 00:11:51.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Communicator beeps ]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-engineering's good to go, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:11:51.627 --> 00:11:53.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You've got full impulse</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and warp standing by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

207
00:11:54.255 --> 00:11:57.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, Travis.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Let's hitch a ride to Mars.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:11:57.967 --> 00:11:59.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:21.949 --> 00:12:23.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Thank you for seeing me.</i></c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:23.159 --> 00:12:24.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's so urgent?</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:25.828 --> 00:12:26.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I never got my lawyer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:27.496 --> 00:12:28.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You'll have to talk to the captain.</i></c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:28.747 --> 00:12:30.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Apparently, he's busy.</i></c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:30.166 --> 00:12:31.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all are.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:33.127 --> 00:12:34.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:35.671 --> 00:12:37.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I don't work for Terra prime.</i></c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:42.344 --> 00:12:44.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I work for Starfleet intelligence.</i></c.bg_transparent>

218
00:12:45.764 --> 00:12:46.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not possible.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:12:47.016 --> 00:12:48.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Scoffs ]</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:12:49.935 --> 00:12:52.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are not the only one</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who wants to serve his people.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:54.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you were an S.I. Agent,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'd be out of this brig</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:12:54.148 --> 00:12:55.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With one call to your division head.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:12:56.066 --> 00:12:58.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And everyone on </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would know who I am,</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:12:58.652 --> 00:13:01.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>including the real Terra prime operative.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:13:03.782 --> 00:13:05.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Communicator beeps ]</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:13:05.951 --> 00:13:08.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mayweather. Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:08.662 --> 00:13:10.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Malcolm ] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We're ready for you</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in the launch bay.</i></c.bg_transparent>

228
00:13:11.081 --> 00:13:11.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:15.586 --> 00:13:17.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know I'm going to tell</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the captain about this.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:17.922 --> 00:13:19.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He won't believe you.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:20.508 --> 00:13:21.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Probably not.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:21.634 --> 00:13:23.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why--why are you telling me this now?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:23.928 --> 00:13:25.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going after Paxton.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:27.014 --> 00:13:29.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If someone on Enterprise</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is working for him,</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:30.392 --> 00:13:31.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he could know you're coming.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:31.644 --> 00:13:35.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you're revealing all of this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because you're worried about me.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:13:35.814 --> 00:13:36.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:13:38.234 --> 00:13:39.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm touched.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:13:39.777 --> 00:13:41.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis, wait!</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:13:42.279 --> 00:13:44.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to manipulate me again.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:13:45.032 --> 00:13:45.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Goodbye.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:13:55.334 --> 00:13:57.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep the sensors locked on the array.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:13:57.461 --> 00:13:58.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The moment it powers up--</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:13:59.046 --> 00:14:00.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't hesitate, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:02.049 --> 00:14:05.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when you used to jump</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every time the engines hiccuped.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:05.386 --> 00:14:08.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I still do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just better at hiding it.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:08.973 --> 00:14:10.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:13.227 --> 00:14:15.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't get too used to that chair.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:15.312 --> 00:14:16.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm gonna want it back.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:16.981 --> 00:14:17.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Understood.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:26.991 --> 00:14:31.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I never used to like Vulcans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all that much myself.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:33.414 --> 00:14:37.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They always seemed so smug,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>making us jump through hoops</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:37.710 --> 00:14:40.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For every little advance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in warp technology,</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:40.880 --> 00:14:42.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they knew the answers all along.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:43.549 --> 00:14:44.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what was it with you?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:46.051 --> 00:14:49.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ears?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The fact that they're vegetarian?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:14:50.389 --> 00:14:51.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're not human.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:14:51.891 --> 00:14:54.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, can't deny that.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:14:54.810 --> 00:14:57.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And they sat by while millions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our people died.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:14:59.398 --> 00:15:00.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>World War III.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:00.357 --> 00:15:03.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't make contact with the Vulcans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until 10 years after the war.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:03.777 --> 00:15:07.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they were up there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with their superior technology.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:15:07.114 --> 00:15:09.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They could have stopped it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but they didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:15:10.659 --> 00:15:11.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it suited their plans.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:15:12.286 --> 00:15:14.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A devastated Earth was much easier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for them to control.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:15.915 --> 00:15:18.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that the kind of paranoid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>crap Paxton's been feeding you?</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:19.460 --> 00:15:20.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get back to work.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:24.548 --> 00:15:26.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You ever actually met a Vulcan?</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:27.134 --> 00:15:29.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your friend, she's the first.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:33.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you got to know some,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Actually took the time to talk with one,</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:33.933 --> 00:15:36.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>yeah, well, you obviously</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>did more than talk.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:36.977 --> 00:15:41.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And look what you got for your trouble.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Some half-Human thing.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:43.233 --> 00:15:44.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Scoffs ]</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:44.610 --> 00:15:45.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:49.448 --> 00:15:50.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:15:50.449 --> 00:15:51.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ugh!</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:58.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Grunting ]</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:15:58.791 --> 00:16:00.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a traitor.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:01.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Groaning ]</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:02.503 --> 00:16:04.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A traitor to humanity.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:17.309 --> 00:16:19.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Rumbling ]</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:16:24.483 --> 00:16:27.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull plating's steady at 94%.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:16:27.319 --> 00:16:28.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:28.946 --> 00:16:30.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with the inertial dampeners?</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:30.864 --> 00:16:33.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need to maintain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an erratic flight profile</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:33.367 --> 00:16:35.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So we look like a chunk of the comet.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:36.203 --> 00:16:37.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:39.206 --> 00:16:40.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thirty minutes to the atmosphere.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:42.543 --> 00:16:44.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm taking us closer to the nucleus.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:44.211 --> 00:16:46.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to start getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little rough.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:46.213 --> 00:16:47.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Start?</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:16:47.464 --> 00:16:49.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you like me to give you something?</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:49.508 --> 00:16:51.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, I've already had the maximum dosage.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:51.427 --> 00:16:54.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Here's a bag.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Grunts ]</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:54.096 --> 00:16:58.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing aliens like better</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Than to see us fighting one another.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:16:58.142 --> 00:17:00.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where's T'Pol and the baby?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-They're together.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:00.436 --> 00:17:03.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll eat as soon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as you finish your work.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:03.564 --> 00:17:04.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am finished.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:05.190 --> 00:17:07.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All you've done is try to sabotage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the targeting system.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:07.901 --> 00:17:09.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:09.528 --> 00:17:11.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please. I've been monitoring your work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the control center.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:11.739 --> 00:17:16.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest, I'd have been disappointed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you hadn't tried to sabotage the array.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:16.493 --> 00:17:19.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you did. Which proves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're a man of principle.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:19.329 --> 00:17:22.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why I know you're going to refine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the array just as you promised.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:23.208 --> 00:17:26.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you I'd make modifications</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your ship, not your weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:27.755 --> 00:17:30.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In two hours, I am going to fire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Verteron beam</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:30.257 --> 00:17:32.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Directly at Starfleet command.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:32.634 --> 00:17:36.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, with this targeting system</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way it is, I will hit Starfleet,</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:36.263 --> 00:17:39.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'll also take out half</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of San Francisco along with it.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:39.516 --> 00:17:42.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need a scalpel, not a bludgeon.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:17:42.311 --> 00:17:43.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't care what you need.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:17:47.232 --> 00:17:50.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Starfleet's been warned,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if that's what concerns you.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:17:50.861 --> 00:17:52.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, you can either help me,</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:17:52.529 --> 00:17:54.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And a few empty buildings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be destroyed,</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:17:55.491 --> 00:17:57.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or you refuse me, and millions may die.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:17:58.202 --> 00:18:01.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told Starfleet when you're planning</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to fire the array.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:01.497 --> 00:18:04.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you don't think they're gonna blast</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This facility off the face of the planet?</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:10.172 --> 00:18:14.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're so eager for a bloodbath,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a bloodbath is what you will get.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:15.344 --> 00:18:19.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put him in detention.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And make sure he has a news screen.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:22.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want him to see the bodies when</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they start to pull them from the rubble.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:25.813 --> 00:18:26.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hello.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:18:30.359 --> 00:18:31.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your mother.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:36.115 --> 00:18:41.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to need a name.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We should discuss that with your father.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:11.233 --> 00:19:13.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The gravity's starting to tear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the comet apart.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:17.406 --> 00:19:20.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're picking up ionization</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the upper atmosphere.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:29.668 --> 00:19:32.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Whooshing ]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What was that?</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:32.379 --> 00:19:34.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The engine shut down,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but there were no warning lights.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:35.382 --> 00:19:37.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The console's locked up.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:38.302 --> 00:19:40.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:40.387 --> 00:19:41.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull plating's offline.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:45.642 --> 00:19:48.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull temperature's climbing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're coming in too hot.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:02.659 --> 00:20:04.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Travis ] Bypassing auto flight control.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:06.288 --> 00:20:07.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Switching to manual.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:20:07.414 --> 00:20:08.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Malcolm ] At this speed?</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:20:08.749 --> 00:20:10.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Travis ] We're out of options.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:20:15.756 --> 00:20:19.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ground proximity?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Archer ] Five seconds to impact.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:20:33.232 --> 00:20:36.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that was fun.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Can we do it again?</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:20:40.530 --> 00:20:41.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Grunts ]</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:03.220 --> 00:21:05.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:42.592 --> 00:21:43.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A mark 3 interlock.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:22:05.574 --> 00:22:09.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The closer we get, the more we risk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Being spotted by Paxton's sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:22:10.829 --> 00:22:15.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Get close to that ridge line.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I was thinking the same thing.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:22:15.542 --> 00:22:19.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll want to keep your arms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inside the vehicle at all times.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:22:36.563 --> 00:22:38.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Malcolm ] Thirty two.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Phlox ] Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:22:39.066 --> 00:22:42.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Malcolm ] This is the 32nd planet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've set foot on.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:22:42.569 --> 00:22:44.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Phlox ] Two hundred forty eight.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:22:46.364 --> 00:22:49.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Archer ] The Verteron array</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is on the other side of that rise.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:22:49.576 --> 00:22:50.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll head through there.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:22:57.751 --> 00:22:59.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Paxton ] I'm told you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have something to say to me.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:23:00.295 --> 00:23:03.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-In private.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I keep no secrets from my men.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:23:04.466 --> 00:23:07.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and I both know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's not true.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:23:11.139 --> 00:23:12.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Josiah, give us the room.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:23:13.308 --> 00:23:14.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be outside.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:23:20.774 --> 00:23:24.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My daughter's ill.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You'll arrange for medical care at once.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:23:25.529 --> 00:23:27.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one leaves this facility.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:23:27.697 --> 00:23:30.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You will provide immediate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>transport for my child,</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:23:30.617 --> 00:23:32.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Tucker, and myself.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:23:32.494 --> 00:23:35.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hospital at Utopia colony</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be suitable</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:23:35.205 --> 00:23:36.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>arrives.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:23:36.998 --> 00:23:38.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Chuckles ]</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:23:38.708 --> 00:23:41.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What, have you been inhaling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the atmosphere?</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:23:41.920 --> 00:23:44.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you think you can dictate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>terms to me?</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:23:45.173 --> 00:23:46.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:23:48.009 --> 00:23:49.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Taggart's syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:23:50.345 --> 00:23:54.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since you obviously didn't die by age 20,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're receiving treatment.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:23:57.060 --> 00:23:59.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Rigellian gene therapy?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You're not a doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:23:59.646 --> 00:24:03.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The very thing you're warning humans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to avoid is what's keeping you alive.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:24:04.109 --> 00:24:06.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alien knowledge, freely shared.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:24:06.528 --> 00:24:09.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not only a terrorist,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're a hypocrite.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:24:09.156 --> 00:24:11.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is not the time for timidity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and second-guessing.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:24:11.575 --> 00:24:13.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We cannot afford to doubt ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:24:13.827 --> 00:24:16.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Colonel Green also said,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"to be Human is to be pure."</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:24:16.997 --> 00:24:18.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Under his rule,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:24:18.248 --> 00:24:20.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you would have been euthanized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for having a genetic disorder.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:24:20.333 --> 00:24:22.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the first significant leader</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:24:22.252 --> 00:24:24.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who failed to measure up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his own ideals.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:24:24.671 --> 00:24:26.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not significant.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:24:26.214 --> 00:24:28.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>History will determine that!</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:24:28.508 --> 00:24:30.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Tell my followers what you wish.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:24:31.011 --> 00:24:33.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>See if they take the word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of an alien over mine.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:24:36.641 --> 00:24:38.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with your child?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:24:38.602 --> 00:24:41.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elevated white blood cell count,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>low-grade fever.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:24:42.147 --> 00:24:46.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, its two halves are warring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with one another.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:24:46.193 --> 00:24:49.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alien and human. Conflict was inevitable.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:24:51.489 --> 00:24:52.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Josiah.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:24:57.078 --> 00:24:59.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your child and the coalition of planets</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:25:01.583 --> 00:25:03.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>both doomed from the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:25:06.296 --> 00:25:07.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:25:08.215 --> 00:25:09.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Malcolm ] Ten meters.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:25:24.731 --> 00:25:26.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Paxton's deadline is up.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:25:27.275 --> 00:25:31.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to face an unpleasant reality.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Archer's mission has failed.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:25:31.655 --> 00:25:34.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Paxton will need two minutes to power up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the array before he can fire.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:25:34.491 --> 00:25:35.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Two minutes?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's enough.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:25:36.034 --> 00:25:39.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not prepared to take that chance.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Your estimates could be wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:25:39.746 --> 00:25:42.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't destroy the array unless</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have no other choice.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:25:42.290 --> 00:25:43.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand your reluctance.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:25:43.583 --> 00:25:45.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm following orders.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:25:45.210 --> 00:25:47.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm giving you new orders.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Do it now.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:25:49.297 --> 00:25:52.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sorry, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can have you relieved of duty.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:25:54.928 --> 00:25:57.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I can only be relieved</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by a higher-ranking officer</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:25:57.472 --> 00:25:58.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in my chain of command.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:25:59.057 --> 00:26:01.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel to admiral Gardner.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:26:01.101 --> 00:26:03.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Belay that order.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I won't risk exposing our position</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:26:03.895 --> 00:26:05.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>By breaking radio silence.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:26:06.815 --> 00:26:10.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're risking the lives of hundreds</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of thousands of people.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:26:11.319 --> 00:26:13.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what I'm doing.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:26:25.458 --> 00:26:27.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:26:27.794 --> 00:26:29.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The guard's still walking away.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:26:32.966 --> 00:26:34.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:26:34.426 --> 00:26:36.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's another guard approaching.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:26:42.392 --> 00:26:44.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Took you long enough.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Where's T'Pol?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:26:44.978 --> 00:26:47.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Crew quarters. But Paxton's getting ready</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to fire the array.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:26:47.564 --> 00:26:48.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he powers it up...</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:26:48.732 --> 00:26:50.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>has orders</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy the complex.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:26:54.904 --> 00:26:56.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've spoken to our operatives.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:26:56.865 --> 00:26:58.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no indication that the Vulcans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have withdrawn</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:58.825 --> 00:27:01.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>from their consulates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in Canberra or Berlin.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:27:02.245 --> 00:27:04.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never expected them to comply.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:06.041 --> 00:27:07.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get this done.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:27:09.044 --> 00:27:10.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm picking up a power surge in the array.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:10.837 --> 00:27:14.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're out of time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Destroy the complex now.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:15.258 --> 00:27:17.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take us in, full impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:19.804 --> 00:27:21.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Charge weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:23.725 --> 00:27:25.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Josiah, begin the firing sequence.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:25.518 --> 00:27:26.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:27.020 --> 00:27:28.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Target locked.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:33.860 --> 00:27:35.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give the order.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:37.030 --> 00:27:38.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Coordinates locked in.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:40.116 --> 00:27:42.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Two minutes to pulse activation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:42.786 --> 00:27:44.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Groans ]</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:45.580 --> 00:27:46.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:48.124 --> 00:27:49.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Step away from the controls.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:50.001 --> 00:27:51.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jonathan Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:52.128 --> 00:27:55.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The man who delivered us from the Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Well, look at you now.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:27:55.965 --> 00:27:56.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

436
00:27:57.258 --> 00:27:58.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead, Captain.</i></c.bg_transparent>

437
00:27:58.343 --> 00:27:59.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're inside the control room.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:01.262 --> 00:28:02.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Standing by.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:04.057 --> 00:28:04.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shut it down.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:05.183 --> 00:28:06.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Main controls are in there.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:10.397 --> 00:28:11.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Groans ]</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:12.649 --> 00:28:14.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Alarm blaring ]</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:14.442 --> 00:28:16.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>90 seconds</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to pulse activation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:16.152 --> 00:28:17.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Grunts ]</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:21.533 --> 00:28:25.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Archer ] The room's depressurizing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get Malcolm out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:28.456 --> 00:28:29.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go!</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:48.977 --> 00:28:50.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Plasma grid...</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:28:50.812 --> 00:28:52.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Control panel.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:28:56.276 --> 00:28:58.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know the reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've turned your back on humanity.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:00.196 --> 00:29:01.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I blame your father.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:01.990 --> 00:29:04.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wanted the secrets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of warp technology so badly,</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:04.659 --> 00:29:07.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he allowed the Vulcans to turn him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into their pet human.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:08.079 --> 00:29:11.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you, well, the sins of the father...</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:29:12.041 --> 00:29:13.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:13.251 --> 00:29:17.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Plasma grid off line.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Firing sequence aborted.</i></c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:18.506 --> 00:29:21.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My father never asked anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:21.676 --> 00:29:25.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His mining operations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>transformed the moon...</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:26.598 --> 00:29:30.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From a mere colony</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into a completely self-sufficient world,</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:31.227 --> 00:29:35.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that is how we should</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>go to the stars.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:35.148 --> 00:29:38.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Taking the worlds</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we need and taming them,</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:38.359 --> 00:29:43.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With Human hands and Human minds</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Human souls.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:43.406 --> 00:29:45.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That might have worked</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the moon,</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:46.534 --> 00:29:49.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the galaxy's a lot more crowded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than we thought.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:49.287 --> 00:29:51.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not our problem.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:51.122 --> 00:29:52.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an opportunity.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:54.793 --> 00:29:56.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's over, Paxton.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:57.504 --> 00:29:59.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're each his father's child.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:03.802 --> 00:30:07.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been a miner all my life.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You get used to the low oxygen.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:08.348 --> 00:30:10.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:10.141 --> 00:30:12.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Firing sequence resumed.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Coughing ]</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:12.602 --> 00:30:15.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pulse activation in 30 seconds.</i></c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:16.022 --> 00:30:18.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Both grunting ]</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:24.447 --> 00:30:25.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Beeping ]</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:26.032 --> 00:30:28.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pulse activation in 15 seconds.</i></c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:31.162 --> 00:30:33.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ten, nine, eight, seven, six--</i></c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:33.623 --> 00:30:35.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've locked the sequence.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:35.333 --> 00:30:36.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't stop it from firing.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:37.043 --> 00:30:38.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Five, four...</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've locked it!</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:39.045 --> 00:30:42.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Three, two, one.</i></c.bg_transparent>

480
00:30:44.634 --> 00:30:46.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pulse activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:47.053 --> 00:30:49.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Breathing heavily ]</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:49.597 --> 00:30:52.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terra prime forever.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:31:02.277 --> 00:31:04.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Tucker ] Looks like Paxton's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aim was off.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:05.071 --> 00:31:08.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Gasping] with a little help from you.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:08.324 --> 00:31:10.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe a little.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:12.787 --> 00:31:13.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:14.789 --> 00:31:15.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's dying.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:31:25.550 --> 00:31:29.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's star log, January 22, 2155.</i></c.bg_transparent>

489
00:31:29.762 --> 00:31:31.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise is returning to Earth.</i></c.bg_transparent>

490
00:31:32.056 --> 00:31:35.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Paxton is in custody, but</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the consequences of his actions</i></c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:35.685 --> 00:31:37.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Continue to affect us all.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:44.527 --> 00:31:46.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess we shouldn't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>keep calling her "she."</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:48.114 --> 00:31:49.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elizabeth.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:52.535 --> 00:31:54.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My sister would have liked that.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:32:03.922 --> 00:32:07.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It appears my initial prognosis</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was incorrect.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:32:10.094 --> 00:32:11.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's genetic.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:32:12.555 --> 00:32:16.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Her Vulcan and Human</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>DNA aren't compatible.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:32:21.731 --> 00:32:23.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there anything you can do?</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:32:23.483 --> 00:32:26.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm attempting to stabilize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>her nucleotides,</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:26.611 --> 00:32:29.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's never been a child like her.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:31.115 --> 00:32:32.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Her name is Elizabeth.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:35.703 --> 00:32:37.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't figure out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why the console locked up</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:37.455 --> 00:32:39.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At the same time the engines shut down.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:40.458 --> 00:32:42.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does seem a bit coincidental.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:32:42.961 --> 00:32:44.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Sighs ]</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:32:46.089 --> 00:32:49.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Flight control and engine power</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are routed separately</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:32:50.176 --> 00:32:52.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until they reach...</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:32:54.889 --> 00:32:56.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That junction.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:32:56.557 --> 00:32:58.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The panel's open.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:32:58.434 --> 00:33:00.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If ionized gas got in here,</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:33:00.353 --> 00:33:02.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It could have melted the primary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>circuits of both systems.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:33:02.855 --> 00:33:05.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It could have been knocked loose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by an impact.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:33:05.108 --> 00:33:07.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[Beeping]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No. It's been forced.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:33:08.361 --> 00:33:09.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This was deliberate.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:33:10.780 --> 00:33:11.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Door chimes ]</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:33:11.781 --> 00:33:12.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:33:14.450 --> 00:33:15.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On your feet, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:33:17.328 --> 00:33:20.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shuttlepod 1 was sabotaged.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:33:20.206 --> 00:33:22.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sabotaged?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-We nearly crashed!</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:22.667 --> 00:33:25.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is this your signature?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:26.713 --> 00:33:29.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You think I had something to do with it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Is there any reason why we shouldn't?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:30.049 --> 00:33:31.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a shuttlepod maintenance log.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:33:31.926 --> 00:33:35.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Tucker took me off that team</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>When he came back from </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Columbia.</i></c.bg_transparent>

524
00:33:35.888 --> 00:33:37.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who replaced you?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:33:38.349 --> 00:33:40.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Who?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Ensign Masaro.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:33:45.565 --> 00:33:47.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They really want to postpone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the conference?</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:33:47.859 --> 00:33:51.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Postpone" is a diplomatic way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of saying it's dead.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:51.154 --> 00:33:53.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Paxton's unnerved them,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and there's not a lot</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:53.239 --> 00:33:55.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been able to say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to change their minds.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:55.241 --> 00:33:57.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[ Communicator beeps ]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Excuse me, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:58.161 --> 00:33:59.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sato. Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:59.704 --> 00:34:03.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Archer.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Are you still with Samuels?</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:34:03.207 --> 00:34:04.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in the mess hall.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:34:04.876 --> 00:34:06.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is ensign Masaro there?</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:34:10.256 --> 00:34:11.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I don't see him, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:34:12.008 --> 00:34:13.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We think Masaro may be working</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Terra Prime.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:34:14.093 --> 00:34:15.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Samuels may be in danger.</i></c.bg_transparent>

538
00:34:15.636 --> 00:34:17.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reed and Mayweather are on their way.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:34:19.265 --> 00:34:20.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait here, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:34:24.312 --> 00:34:26.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Samuels is in here.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's safe.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:34:29.692 --> 00:34:30.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:34:32.945 --> 00:34:33.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Gasps ]</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:34:35.031 --> 00:34:37.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't want to do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I have to.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:34:39.535 --> 00:34:41.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me the phase pistol.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:42.997 --> 00:34:44.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an order.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:44.457 --> 00:34:45.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:47.001 --> 00:34:48.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:48.211 --> 00:34:49.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted you to know...</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:51.464 --> 00:34:52.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:54.759 --> 00:34:56.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believed in what we were doing.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:58.679 --> 00:35:01.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell my parents I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:35:01.307 --> 00:35:03.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Sobbing ]</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:35:03.267 --> 00:35:05.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never wanted anyone to get hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:35:06.687 --> 00:35:08.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:35:08.147 --> 00:35:09.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Laser fire ]</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:35:09.232 --> 00:35:10.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Thuds ]</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:35:24.664 --> 00:35:26.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I could do more.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:35:27.250 --> 00:35:28.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:35:29.335 --> 00:35:31.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When you invited me to join this crew,</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:35:31.337 --> 00:35:35.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it would be an interesting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>diversion for a few months.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:35:36.175 --> 00:35:39.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some time away from</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the complications of family,</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:35:39.345 --> 00:35:42.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which on Denebola</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can be extremely complicated.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:46.352 --> 00:35:48.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't expect to gain another family.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:55.153 --> 00:35:57.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It hurts as if she were my own child.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:36:08.374 --> 00:36:10.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make something good</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>come from this, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:36:21.512 --> 00:36:24.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fellow delegates, this last week,</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:36:24.724 --> 00:36:28.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we've seen what humans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can be at their worst.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:36:28.269 --> 00:36:30.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we cannot, we must not</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:36:31.063 --> 00:36:35.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>use that as an excuse to end</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the dream that began here.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:36:36.736 --> 00:36:40.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For then the demons</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our past will have won.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:36:41.949 --> 00:36:44.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Instead, I want to look to the future</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:36:45.036 --> 00:36:47.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And begin by honoring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the people responsible</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:36:47.580 --> 00:36:49.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for our being here tonight.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:36:50.249 --> 00:36:53.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They represent all of us at our best.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:37:00.927 --> 00:37:03.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Up until about 100 years ago,</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:37:04.805 --> 00:37:07.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was one question</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that burned in every human</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:37:08.434 --> 00:37:11.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That made us study the stars</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and dream of traveling to them.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:37:14.732 --> 00:37:15.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are we alone?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:37:17.109 --> 00:37:20.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our generation is privileged...</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:37:21.739 --> 00:37:23.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To know the answer to that question.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:37:26.452 --> 00:37:27.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are all explorers,</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:37:28.704 --> 00:37:31.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>driven to know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's over the horizon,</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:37:32.875 --> 00:37:35.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's beyond our own shores?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:37:37.713 --> 00:37:38.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yet...</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:37:43.052 --> 00:37:44.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The more I've experienced...</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:37:46.847 --> 00:37:49.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The more I've learned...</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:37:50.142 --> 00:37:52.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That no matter how far we travel...</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:37:53.938 --> 00:37:55.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or how fast we get there...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:37:58.109 --> 00:38:00.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The most profound discoveries</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:38:01.320 --> 00:38:06.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are not necessarily beyond that next star.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:38:09.787 --> 00:38:14.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're within us...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Woven into the threads that bind us...</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:38:17.128 --> 00:38:20.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of us... to each other.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:38:23.801 --> 00:38:28.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The final frontier begins in this hall.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:38:31.058 --> 00:38:32.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's explore it together.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:39:01.088 --> 00:39:03.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear the conference is back on track.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:39:03.424 --> 00:39:05.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a first step. The captain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>says it's going to take years</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:39:06.010 --> 00:39:07.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To work out the details.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:39:08.012 --> 00:39:11.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it'll happen,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you're part of the reason why.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:39:11.599 --> 00:39:12.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just doing my job.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:39:13.100 --> 00:39:14.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So was I.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:39:18.731 --> 00:39:19.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:39:23.444 --> 00:39:27.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Vulcans and Andorians can get along,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'd think we could.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:39:29.408 --> 00:39:31.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lot of details to work out.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:39:35.623 --> 00:39:37.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't that the fast way home?</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:39:39.335 --> 00:39:42.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The least I can do is give you a ride.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:39:45.508 --> 00:39:47.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The launch bay's this way.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:39:59.271 --> 00:40:00.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Door chimes ]</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:40:02.400 --> 00:40:03.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:40:11.951 --> 00:40:13.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:40:14.662 --> 00:40:16.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Delegates at the conference,</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:40:16.539 --> 00:40:19.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've, uh, asked</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the service for, um...</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:40:24.839 --> 00:40:26.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For Elizabeth.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:40:26.882 --> 00:40:28.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They want to attend.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:40:30.177 --> 00:40:31.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She was important.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:40:32.805 --> 00:40:35.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Sighs ] There's something else.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:40:37.059 --> 00:40:39.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Sniffles ] I spoke with Phlox.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:40:43.983 --> 00:40:47.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It turns out there was a--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a flaw in the technique</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:40:47.445 --> 00:40:53.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That Paxton's doctors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>used in the cloning process.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:40:56.412 --> 00:40:57.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Clears throat ]</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:40:57.872 --> 00:41:01.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Human DNA and Vulcan DNA...</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:41:02.418 --> 00:41:07.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Phlox says there's no medical</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>reason why they can't combine.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:41:10.843 --> 00:41:11.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So...</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:41:12.678 --> 00:41:15.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If a Vulcan and a human...</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:41:17.016 --> 00:41:19.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ever decided to have a child...</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:41:23.939 --> 00:41:26.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It'd probably be okay.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:41:31.363 --> 00:41:32.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[ Sniffles ]</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:41:35.326 --> 00:41:36.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that's sort of comforting.</c.bg_transparent>

